file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: test
  version: 1.0.0
servers:
  - url: /test
    variables: { }
paths:
  /ThisIsEndpoint:
    post:
      summary: TestCalc
      description: "Test text"
      operationId: BlaBlaBla
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/WrapperObject'
      responses:
        "200":
          description: "Test response"
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                type: string
components:
  schemas:
    InnerObject:
      type: object
      properties:
        text:
          type: string
        birthDate:
          type: string
          format: date-time
    WrapperObject:
      type: object
      properties:
        input:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/InnerObject'

Error: notImplemented: path "/ThisIsEndpoint": post: responses: 200: contents: unsupported content types: [text/plain]
